#: ../../sandbox-permissions.rst:2
msgid "Sandbox Permissions"
msgstr "샌드박스 권한"

#: ../../sandbox-permissions.rst:4
msgid ""
"Sandbox permissions can be configured from an application manifest (see :doc:"
"`manifests`). They can also be set with the ``build-finish``, ``run`` and "
"``override`` commands."
msgstr ""
"샌드박스 권한은 응용프로그램의 manifest파일에서 설정할 수 있다(:doc:"
"`manifests` 참조). 또한 ``build-finish``, ``run``, ``override``명령을 이용하"
"여 설정할 수 있다."

#: ../../sandbox-permissions.rst:7
msgid "Permission options"
msgstr "권한 옵션"

#: ../../sandbox-permissions.rst:9
msgid ""
"The following list includes some of the most useful permission options. The "
"full list can be viewed using ``flatpak build-finish --help``"
